Package org.forgerock.openidm.quartz.impl

Class RepoJobStore

java.lang.Object
org.forgerock.openidm.quartz.impl.RepoJobStore
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClusterEventListener, org.quartz.spi.JobStore
public class RepoJobStore extends Object implements org.quartz.spi.JobStore, ClusterEventListener
A JobStore implementation used for persistence with the OpenIdm Repository Service.
